This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and specifically focuses on text categorization tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning techniques and models, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of large datasets and data preprocessing, which could be relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
